      • createAgencyPromiseWithInvoiceItemsMismatch

        public static AgencyCyclePromise createAgencyPromiseWithInvoiceItemsMismatch(StatementInvoice statementInvoice,
                                                             java.util.List<com.google.gdata.util.common.base.Pair<MonetaryAmount,MonetaryAmount>> mismatches)
        Creates an AgencyCyclePromise will all the items as mismatch exceptions. The list provided is used to determine how much to mismatch the gross and commission amount, one pair is used for each item. If there are too few pairs on the mismatches list, the last pair will be used for all further invoice items.
        Parameters:
        statementInvoice - the statement invoice that holds the invoice items
        mismatches - a MonetaryAmount pair: first value = gross shortfall, second value = extra commission withheld
        Returns:
        An AgencyCyclePromise with the appropriate exception items

      • createAndExecuteAgencyPromiseThatWouldFullyPayStatementAndHasOneSuspenseItem

        public static AgencyCyclePromise createAndExecuteAgencyPromiseThatWouldFullyPayStatementAndHasOneSuspenseItem(StatementInvoice statementInvoice,
                                                                                              MonetaryAmount netAmountToSuspense,
                                                                                              MonetaryAmount commissionAmountToSuspense)
        Creates and executes an AgencyCyclePromise that has one AgencySuspPromiseItem -- assumes that we will pay the full statement amount and use policy number "11111". Also uses net amount instead of gross amount, for calling ease in some cases. Uses identical signature as createAgencyPaymentWithSuspenseItem() on AgencyPaymentTestHelper.
        Parameters:
        statementInvoice - target statement of the promise
        netAmountToSuspense - the net amount of the single AgencySuspPromiseItem on the promise
        commissionAmountToSuspense - commission amount of the single AgencySuspPromiseItem on the promise
        Returns:
        an AgencyCyclePromise whose AgencySuspDist contains a single AgencySuspPromiseItem
